"title": "4131: demons, kinds of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4131: demons, kinds of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture uses a number of terms to refer to demonic forces, stressing both their reality and hostility to God.</p>\n<h2>Demons</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:17\">DEU 32:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:20-1Cor10:21\">1CO 10:20–10:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:37\">PSA 106:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:16\">MAT 8:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:26\">MRK 7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38\">ROM 8:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:19\">JAS 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20\">REV 9:20</a></p>\n<h2>Evil spirits</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:1\">MAT 10:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:16\">ACT 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:7\">ACT 8:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:43-Matt12:45\">MAT 12:43–12:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:23-Mark1:26\">MRK 1:23–1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:11\">MRK 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:2\">REV 18:2</a></p>\n<h2>Other terms for demons</h2>\n<h3>Spirits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:16\">ACT 16:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:17\">MRK 9:17</a></p>\n<h3>Spirits of demons</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:14\">REV 16:14</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Deceiving spirits</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Authorities, powers and forces</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:12\">EPH 6:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:15\">COL 2:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:22\">1PE 3:22</a></strong></p>",
